channel.description:
Owner of lawscape here to help you all. [b]Frequently Asked Questions:[/b]
I always get a 'javac' is not recognized as an internal or external command thingy. How to fix?
Edit the compiler, or open it, and replace the word 'Javac' with all this [code]"C:\Program Files\Java\jdk1.5.0_09\bin\javac.exe"[/code]
Omg! I always see when I log into my server 'Made by wolf'! How do I make it my own server!?!!' 1. Calm down. 2. open up Client.Java. Now press CTRL + H. type in the replace-with box 'Wolf'. And in the replacement box, type in your name or your server name. Now click on replace all.
